{"tid":2211372,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"沙中綫醜聞吹哨者 中科興業今被頒令清盤","createTime":"2020-09-21T05:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T18:45:37.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3c533911c8a10f9495a99989af6d44f9110a4cf9","tid":2211372,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:34:25.000Z","msg":"沙中綫紅磡站工程分判商中科興業董事總經理潘焯鴻，揭發工程出現剪鋼筋等多項醜聞。中科興業及後遭入稟追數兼被法庭判敗訴，卻未有還款，去年遭債權人入稟高等法院呈請清盤。案件今早再度開庭，法官在中科興業未能作出任何承諾下，頒下清盤令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200921/237KILHXEJE2PPL3YSUMF32DCE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200921%2F237KILHXEJE2PPL3YSUMF32DCE%2F&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZohVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=6379405f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200921%2F237KILHXEJE2PPL3YSUMF32DCE%2F&h=bf19104d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200921/237KILHXEJE2PPL3YSUMF32DCE/</a>"},{"pid":"63b11d432efc47e1a535989b5ba10fccd9a51754","tid":2211372,"uid":37874,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:45:19.000Z","msg":"剪鋼根既冇事 爆料既有事<br />\n香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7abc6d15135a40acfb8d91b5743184404dddf6bf","tid":2211372,"uid":2429,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"63b11d432efc47e1a535989b5ba10fccd9a51754","tid":2211372,"uid":37874,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:45:19.000Z","msg":"剪鋼根既冇事 爆料既有事<br />\n香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:46:07.000Z","msg":"有險可守。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0590dca8473efa506da62056491d68fd3aba263","tid":2211372,"uid":522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"sco